japanese: あら、ももちゃん！/部室で出し物の準備？
english: Oh, Momo-chan! /Prepping your event in the club room?

japanese: あら！　夏じゃない。/沖田先生と、なに話してたの？
english: Oh! Natsu. /What were you talking about with Okita-sensei?

japanese: あれ、委員長じゃない。/今ヒマなの？
english: Hmm, it's the Chairperson. /Are you free?

japanese: あれが……生徒会室ですか？
あはは！　違うわよ！/バレーボール模様の/普通の大きさのマシュマロよ。
english: Ahaha! That's not it! /It's a volleyball-patterned /regular marshmallow.

japanese: あれ、響子先生。/一人でどうしたんですか？
english: Hmm, Kyoko-sensei. /What are you doing alone?

japanese: あら、バツ……どうしたの？/そんな仏頂面で。
english: Oh, Batsu... what's wrong? /Looking so grumpy.

japanese: ありがとー！/あのお皿、/どうしようか迷ってたんだ。
english: Thanks! /I was wondering what to do /with that plate.

japanese: あれ、委員長じゃない。/ちょうどよかった。/これから私と……
english: Hmm, it's the Chairperson. /Perfect timing. /Now you and I...

japanese: あらら……。/ま、しょうがないか。/邪魔しちゃ悪いしな……。
english: Oh my... /Well, can't be helped. /Don't want to interrupt...

japanese: あらら……。/ま、しょうがないか。/邪魔しちゃ悪いしね……。
english: Oh my... /Well, can't be helped. /Don't want to interrupt...

japanese: あれ、そうだっけ？/去年の話だし、あんまり憶えてないわ。
english: Hmm, was that it? /It was last year, so I don't remember.

japanese: あら……ボーマン。/こんな所に一人でどうしたの？
english: Oh my... Bowman. /What are you doing here alone?

japanese: あら、ひなた。/今日もクラブの助っ人なの？
english: Oh, Hinata. /Helping the club again today?

japanese: あれ、バレてるの？/おっかしいわね。/けっこう自信ある演技だったのに。
english: Hmm, was I found out? /That's strange. /I was confident in my acting.

japanese: あれ、委員長。/そんな大きな袋を抱えて、/一体何やってるの？
english: Hmm, Chairperson. /What are you doing with /such a big bag?

japanese: あれ、委員長。/そんな大きな袋を抱えて、/一体何やってんだ？
english: Hmm, Chairperson. /What are you doing with /such a big bag?
